<sect1 id="ch-system-markupsafe" role="wrap">
  <?dbhtml filename="markupsafe.html"?>

  <sect1info condition="script">
<productname>markupsafe</productname>
<productnumber>&markupsafe-version;</productnumber> <address>&markupsafe-url;</address></sect1info>

  <title>MarkupSafe-&markupsafe-version;</title>

  <indexterm zone="ch-system-markupsafe">
    <primary sortas="a-markupsafe">MarkupSafe</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title/>

    <para>MarkupSafe는 XML/HTML/XHTML에서 안전한 마크업 문자열을 구현하는 파이썬 모듈입니다.</para>

    <segmentedlist>
      <segtitle>&buildtime;</segtitle>
      <segtitle>&diskspace;</segtitle>
      <seglistitem>
        <seg>&markupsafe-fin-sbu;</seg>
        <seg>&markupsafe-fin-du;</seg>
      </seglistitem>
    </segmentedlist>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>MarkupSafe 설치</title>

    <para>다음 명령을 사용하여 MarkupSafe를 컴파일:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="make">pip3 wheel -w dist --no-cache-dir --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

    <para>이 패키지에는 테스트 스위트가 없습니다.</para>

    <para>패키지 설치:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="install">pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist Markupsafe</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 id="contents-markupsafe" role="content">
    <title>MarkupSafe 구성 요소</title>

    <segmentedlist>
      <segtitle>설치된 디렉터리</segtitle>

      <seglistitem>
        <seg>
           /usr/lib/python&python-minor;/site-packages/MarkupSafe-&markupsafe-version;.dist-info
        </seg>
      </seglistitem>
    </segmentedlist>

  </sect2>

</sect1>

